# Trigger rollout by updating annotation (no YAML change needed)
kubectl patch deployment <app> \
  -p '{"spec":{"template":{"metadata":{"annotations":{"date":"'$(date +%s)'"}}}}}'

🧠 Why use this:

When rollout restart is restricted
Forces new ReplicaSet creation
🔹 4. Image Update Without YAML (Hotfix Style)
