kubectl edit deployment <app>

Inside YAML:

strategy:
  type: RollingUpdate
  rollingUpdate:
    maxUnavailable: 1
    maxSurge: 1
🧠 Meaning:
maxUnavailable=1 → 1 pod can go down
maxSurge=1 → 1 extra pod can be created
